cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.SI, cs.CR 

The paper deals with automatic processing of crisis-related social media imagery data using deep learning and perceptual hashing techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) and multimedia (MM) aspects, which makes cs.IR and cs.MM likely categories as well. The paper also deals with security and privacy issues related to crisis data, which makes cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) a possible category. Finally, the paper involves the use of machine learning techniques for real-time processing, which makes cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) a possible category as well.
